title: Data Visualisation
text:
Using data from the NCD, I had show the growth of Singaporean young adults (aged 18) over time. I had decided not to combine the heights of both genders as I realised from initial plotting that there was a big gap between males and females.
From the data, I had discovered that due to improving nutrition availability, youth height steadily increased over time.
I used a line graph to display the height changes over time. Since the 1990s, heights have been steadily improving for both genders, with other sources and research, I concluded that it was due to improving dietary conditions for youths.
